# Agent Handoff

@summary
Ship the docs refresh without changing parser behavior.

@metadata key="owner.team"
docs

@decision id="plain-prose"
Plain top-level text remains the only paragraph source syntax.

@constraint
Do not reintroduce explicit paragraph blocks in source files.

@file path="site/src/content/docs/syntax.lmk"
Owns the public syntax reference.

@api name="parseLessmark"
Parses source into the shared AST.

@task status="doing"
Verify public docs, examples, and packages agree on the same syntax.

@risk level="medium"
Stale examples can teach old syntax even when the parser is correct.

@depends-on target="plain-prose"
Docs must show plain prose instead of an explicit paragraph tag.

@example
# Notes

Plain prose.

@list kind="unordered"
- Explicit list item.
- Another item.

@callout kind="note" title="Agent rule"
Prefer the canonical source spelling.
